      <title>风险资产遭抛售 比特币跌至 11 月以来最低水平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/bitcoin-falls-to-lowest-since-november-in-risk-asset-selloff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于债券收益率大幅上升，投资者抛售风险较高的资产，比特币跌至近两个月来的最低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/bitcoin-falls-to-lowest-since-november-in-risk-asset-selloff</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:43:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能投资者为何应该担心自动驾驶汽车事故</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/why-ai-investors-should-worry-about-the-self-driving-car-crash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[机器人出租车本应是自动化的简单部分。通用汽车的努力失败表明该行业距离实现其疯狂的承诺还有多远。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/why-ai-investors-should-worry-about-the-self-driving-car-crash</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:00:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>白宫公布对英伟达 AI 芯片出口的新限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/white-house-unveils-new-curbs-on-exporting-nvidia-ai-chips</link>
      <description><![CDATA[白宫宣布对英伟达公司及其同行的先进人工智能芯片销售实施全面的新限制，由特朗普政府决定如何以及是否实施遭到业界激烈反对的限制措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/white-house-unveils-new-curbs-on-exporting-nvidia-ai-chips</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
